TextEng: I am <FullName>. I work for Aarin Gend of Neverwinter!
Text: 저는 <FullName>입니다. 네버윈터의 아린 겐드를 위해 일해요!

TextEng: Me am <FullName>. Me work for Aarin Gend.
Text: 나 <FullName>이야. 나 아린 겐드 위해 일해.

TextEng: My name is none of your business!
Text: 내 이름은 네가 알 바 아니야!

TextEng: I had hoped to speak with him.
Why have your sisters taken him?
